  <section>
    <title>Fading LED.</title>

    <para>Demonstrates the use of analog output (Pulse Width Modulation (PWM))
    to fade an LED.</para>

    <para>PWM is a technique for getting an analog-like behavior from a
    digital output by switching it off and on very fast.</para>
  </section>

